public boolean hasSameNameAs(java.lang.String otherChromoName)
Returns true if the name of the current chromosome is equal to the specified string. Removes "chr" and "chromosome" before comparing if the string in parameter or if the chromosome name start this way (ex: "chr1" becomes "1")

Parameters:
